Interaction between frailty and sex on mortality after elective abdominal aortic 
aneurysm repair.

Barbey SM(1), Scali ST(2), Kubilis P(2), Beck AW(3), Goodney P(4), Giles KA(2), 
Berceli SA(2), Huber TS(2), Upchurch GR(2), Yaghjyan L(5).

Author information:
(1)Division of Vascular Surgery and Endovascular Therapy, University of Florida, 
