Excess burden of a chronic disabling condition: life lost due to traumatic 
spinal cord injury in a Swiss population-based cohort study.

Chamberlain JD(1)(2)(3), Buzzell A(4)(5), Gmünder HP(6), Hug K(7), Jordan X(8), 
