Gender-Specific Differences in Concentrations of Biochemical Parameters in 
Persons over the Age of 90.

Zabielska P(1), Wieder-Huszla S(2), Gutowska I(3), Lubkowska A(4), Knyszyńska 
A(5), Jurczak A(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Social Medicine and Public Health, Chair of Social Medicine, 
Pomeranian Medical University in Szczecin, Żołnierska Str. 48, 71-210 Szczecin, 
Poland. paulina.zabielska@pum.edu.pl.
(2)Department of Clinical Nursing, Pomeranian Medical University in Szczecin, 
